Class CallableDistributor.Result<R>

java.lang.Object
  org.threadly.concurrent.CallableDistributor.Result<R>
Type Parameters:
R - result type
Enclosing class:
CallableDistributor<K,R>
public static class CallableDistributor.Result<R>
extends java.lang.Object

Result from a callable which can be either a computed result, or an exception due to failure. These are different from futures in that they represent the product of work, not work that has yet to occur.
